snippet.title: Space Reign - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
PUBLIC DEMO will be released on Feb 6th. Stay tuned!

Wishlist our game on Steam !https://store.steampowered.com/app/1762570/Space_Reign/

Become our patreon and support us on our journey! https://www.patreon.com/propulsivegames

Space Reign is a part space sim, part strategy indie game about fleet combat, management, and completing security contracts for resource exploiting corporations in the near future, which are in a state of constant conflict over territory control.

Check out our discord channel for even more frequent updates ! https://discord.gg/VWeyz74

Music license from artlist.io
